WEBVTT

00:01.100 --> 00:02.632
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...

00:02.635 --> 00:05.742
Seems our dead guy Harvey was
friends with the sirens back in 1790.

00:05.745 --> 00:08.614
Turns out, he was related to
a family from Mystic Falls.

00:08.617 --> 00:09.609
MATT: <i>I got a question for you.</i>

00:09.611 --> 00:11.277
I need you to tell me what this is.

00:11.279 --> 00:13.112
It's a cipher device
used for code-breaking.

00:13.114 --> 00:15.591
When the door between
this world and Cade's

00:15.594 --> 00:16.583
gets cracked open,

00:16.585 --> 00:17.750
it wipes out everything.

00:17.752 --> 00:19.152
SELINE: <i>All you got to do is make sure</i>

00:19.154 --> 00:20.687
<i>that bell rings 12 times.</i>

00:20.689 --> 00:23.957
CADE: <i>The task I gave both
of you was kill 100 people</i>

00:23.959 --> 00:25.225
or kill your brother's girl.

00:25.227 --> 00:26.259
Stefan chose option "B."

00:26.261 --> 00:27.727
Elena's in upstate New York.

00:27.729 --> 00:28.862
<i>That's where Bonnie hid her.</i>

00:28.864 --> 00:29.996
Leave Elena out of this.

00:29.998 --> 00:31.030
Enzo?

00:31.032 --> 00:32.198
[grunts]

00:33.115 --> 00:34.448
[Bonnie screams]

00:34.451 --> 00:36.069
Why do you care what happens to Elena?

00:36.071 --> 00:37.403
You're gonna be dead anyway.

00:37.405 --> 00:38.805
You're gonna be human.

00:38.807 --> 00:40.106
[grunts]

00:41.943 --> 00:43.017
Enzo!

00:44.045 --> 00:47.513
[screaming, sobbing]

00:55.023 --> 00:56.689
[screams]

00:56.691 --> 00:59.259
[bell tolling]

00:59.261 --> 01:02.862
[voices shouting, screaming]

01:07.903 --> 01:09.636
[gasps]

01:11.000 --> 01:17.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:18.813 --> 01:19.946
[groans]

01:26.021 --> 01:28.488
[alarm wailing]

01:38.366 --> 01:40.066
Geez!

01:40.068 --> 01:41.501
Matt?

01:41.503 --> 01:43.791
How'd you get in here?

01:45.840 --> 01:47.173
Are you okay?

01:47.175 --> 01:49.275
No.

01:49.277 --> 01:51.678
Something's wrong with me.

01:51.681 --> 01:57.282
